<% const pageTitle = "Privacy Policy – VK Training Consultency"; %>
<%- include('partials/head') %>
<%- include('partials/navbar') %>

<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-10">Last updated: 25 April 2026</p>

  <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8 text-slate-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">1. Introduction</h2>
      <p>VK Training Consultency ("we", "us", "our") is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains what data we collect, how we use it, and your rights in relation to it, in accordance with the Information Technology Act, 2000 and associated rules.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li><strong>Account data:</strong> name, email address, and hashed password when you register.</li>
        <li><strong>Payment data:</strong> transaction IDs, order IDs, and payment status. We do not store full card numbers or CVV details — these are handled exclusively by Razorpay.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> pages visited, videos watched, session timestamps, and browser/device information.</li>
        <li><strong>Affiliate data:</strong> referral codes, commission records, and payout history if you participate in our affiliate programme.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li>To provide, operate, and improve the Platform.</li>
        <li>To process payments and issue refunds.</li>
        <li>To send transactional emails (purchase confirmations, password resets).</li>
        <li>To calculate and process affiliate commissions.</li>
        <li>To comply with legal obligations and prevent fraud.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">4. Sharing of Information</h2>
      <p>We do not sell your personal data. We share data only with:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li><strong>Razorpay</strong> – for payment processing. Subject to <a href="https://razorpay.com/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Razorpay's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
        <li>Service providers (hosting, email) under confidentiality agreements.</li>
        <li>Law enforcement or regulatory authorities when required by law.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">5. Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use session cookies to keep you logged in and functional cookies to remember preferences. We do not use third-party advertising cookies. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, but this may affect Platform functionality.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">6. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>Account and transaction data is retained for a minimum of 7 years as required by Indian tax regulations. You may request deletion of non-transactional data by contacting us.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">7. Security</h2>
      <p>We implement industry-standard security measures including encrypted connections (HTTPS), bcrypt-hashed passwords, and session management. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">8. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data by emailing us. We will respond within 30 days.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">9. Contact</h2>
      <p><strong>VK Training Consultency</strong><br />
      Email: <a href="mailto:support@vktraining.in" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">support@vktraining.in</a></p>
    </section>

  </div>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
